msgstr ""
"Intertemporal Arbitrage Trading Strategies (Equivalent "
"Educational Version)"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:3
msgid ""
"参考来源：`docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_08_跨期套"
"利.ipynb` 第一个 Markdown cell。"
msgstr ""
"Reference source: `docs/_joinquant_migration_source/"
"Example_08_intertemporal arbitrage.ipynb` First Markdown cell."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:5
msgid "策略思路"
msgstr "Strategy and Ideas"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:7
msgid "使用同品种不同到期合约构造价差；"
msgstr ""
"Construct price spreads using contracts of the same type but with "
"different expiration dates;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:8
msgid "用滚动窗口估计价差偏离程度（zscore）；"
msgstr ""
"Use a rolling window to estimate the degree of price spread "
"deviation (zscore)."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:9
msgid "价差上穿上轨做空价差，下穿下轨做多价差；"
msgstr ""
"Short the spread when it crosses above the upper band, and go "
"long when it crosses below the lower band."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:10
msgid "回归到中性区间时平仓。"
msgstr "Close the position when it returns to the neutral range."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:12
msgid "qteasy 实现说明"
msgstr "QtEasy Implementation Instructions"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:14
msgid "本示例策略类为 `Example08CalendarSpread`；"
msgstr ""
"The strategy class in this example is `Example08CalendarSpread`;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:15
msgid "为了教学稳定性，默认脚本使用指数日频做跨期逻辑近似；"
msgstr ""
"For the sake of teaching stability, the default script uses the "
"daily index frequency for inter-period logical approximation;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_08_跨期套利.md:16
msgid ""
"若切换到真实期货合约，请同时处理换月逻辑，并在文档中记录换月规则。"
msgstr ""
"If switching to a real futures contract, please handle the "
"rollover logic at the same time and record the rollover rules in "
"the documentation."

